# requestDidComplete(_:)

**Instance Method**

Notifies your app when the analysis request completes normally.

## Declaration

```swift
optional func requestDidComplete(_ request: any SNRequest)
```

## Parameters

- **request**: The request thatâ€™s completing.

## Discussion

The analyzer calls this method when it finishes processing the request.

## Handling Requests

- **request(_:didProduce:)**: Provides a new analysis result to your app with the specified time range.
- **SNResult**: A protocol that represents sound analysis results.
- **request(_:didFailWithError:)**: Provides any errors that occur during processing of the request.
